 at low energy could not be confirmed. The present\nextrapolated zero-energy S-factors are $S_{6.79}(0)$~=~1.24$\\pm$0.11~keV~barn\nand $S_{\\rm GS}(0)$~=~0.19$\\pm$0.05~keV~barn.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Nov 2017 13:45:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-08"}
