that when all the valuations are i.i.d., it is further equivalent\nto that separate-selling is optimal. In particular, it respects one result from\nthe recent breakthrough work on the exact optimal solutions in the multi-item\nmulti-buyer setting by Yao [2016].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Nov 2017 15:37:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-30"}
